{"tid":1627783,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我覺得自己好失敗⋯⋯","createTime":"2019-10-05T17:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T15:04:06.000Z","uid":318768,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d9d0f6e5ff3a5e78de171513ea937b0f8bd18b23","tid":1627783,"uid":318768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:51:06.000Z","msg":"黎緊廿歲女，讀asso<br />\nA0<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大眾樣又肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老豆爭人錢，老母出軌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我之前為咗幫老豆還錢爭落一大筆卡數<br />\n全家都有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢地好愛我，但覺得自己好撚冇用<br />\n香港又搞成咁，自己乜都做唔到咁，冇力感好重，覺得自己好垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好似做乜都唔開心咁⋯⋯<br />\nBTW唯一有樣好，就係全家都深黃<br />\nsor for 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63870f727fd2db37cd73444e3b1e013f6dea1b8","tid":1627783,"uid":307619,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:51:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">毋忘721 831</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3P10Kbc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3P10Kbc.jpg&h=66ce219c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6gDivRd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6gDivRd.jpg&h=9e847180&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3ZFHXwd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3ZFHXwd.jpg&h=68a9a8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tKXZZKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtKXZZKz.jpg&h=933e09df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bf28cdb19c51e61f0795fda8f03b540464e40f3","tid":1627783,"uid":157735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T17:52:19.000Z","msg":"加油 出去發夢